title: The Future Sound of London - Other Aliases Discography [FLAC]
description:
Part 3 of a 4 part series compiling the works of Brian Dougans and Garry Cobain, known to most as the Future Sound of London. This torrent contains works of theirs released under their lesser-known pseudonyms. Enjoy and seed!

Please note: These releases are included in FLAC whenever possible, but several of them, which are marked below, were only sold digitally in MP3 format.
